WEBVTT

00:13.160 --> 00:16.309
[Tangjing]

00:28.280 --> 00:29.280
We split up.

00:30.190 --> 00:31.760
You go find out where everyone is.

00:31.760 --> 00:33.270
I'll enter the palace to see the Empress

00:33.270 --> 00:35.000
and try to find out something about Li Ce.

00:35.000 --> 00:36.800
The Empress is deeply inscrutable.

00:36.800 --> 00:38.060
Be careful on your own.

00:42.730 --> 00:46.400
[Qingfen Restaurant]

02:05.890 --> 02:11.000
[REBIRTH]

02:11.510 --> 02:14.070
[Episode 17]

02:16.000 --> 02:17.120
I'm Princess Fu.

02:17.280 --> 02:20.010
I'd like to request an audience
with Her Majesty.

02:20.310 --> 02:23.060
[Linrui Palace]

02:29.400 --> 02:30.860
Greetings, Your Majesty.

02:49.280 --> 02:50.030
Chun'er?

02:50.590 --> 02:53.050
I've been expecting you
for quite some time.

02:53.079 --> 02:56.190
But I'm afraid
you can no longer call me "Chun'er."

02:56.430 --> 02:58.840
You should address me as
"Princess Consort of Luo."

02:58.840 --> 03:00.040
Where is Her Majesty?

03:00.250 --> 03:01.780
She doesn't want to see you.

03:02.190 --> 03:03.520
She sent me in her place.

03:03.520 --> 03:04.310
In that case,

03:04.680 --> 03:05.880
I shall take my leave.

03:06.400 --> 03:07.280
Why the rush?

03:07.590 --> 03:10.650
You're about to be married off
to Great Yan as its Queen.

03:12.030 --> 03:14.890
I've had some fine wine
specially prepared for you.

03:15.150 --> 03:16.910
Why don't we celebrate first?

03:17.400 --> 03:18.400
Think of it

03:18.630 --> 03:20.710
as an early toast
to your upcoming wedding.

03:20.710 --> 03:21.640
What did you say?

03:29.120 --> 03:30.180
Queen of Great Yan.

03:33.870 --> 03:35.030
Don't you know?

03:35.560 --> 03:38.000
Yan Xun has come here
to seek your hand in marriage,

03:38.000 --> 03:39.960
and Her Majesty has already approved.

03:39.960 --> 03:40.910
Your dowry

03:40.910 --> 03:43.360
has already been sent to
the Crown Prince's Mansion.

03:43.360 --> 03:45.240
You don't need to
worry about Li Ce anymore.

03:45.240 --> 03:47.650
You may not become
Crown Princess of Biantang,

03:47.650 --> 03:51.050
but very soon
you'll be Queen of Great Yan.

03:51.710 --> 03:52.190
Come on.

03:53.360 --> 03:54.290
Let me teach you.

03:55.240 --> 03:57.960
On your wedding night,
drink the crossed-cup wine

03:57.960 --> 04:00.310
with Yan Xun like this.

04:06.590 --> 04:08.790
This is how the Prince of Luo and I
did it.

04:12.510 --> 04:14.710
The idea of marrying me off to Great Yan—

04:15.030 --> 04:16.490
that was your suggestion.

04:16.829 --> 04:18.240
Quite clever of you.

04:19.920 --> 04:21.519
Aren't you going to thank me?

04:22.430 --> 04:24.430
You and Yan Xun are so deeply in love.

04:25.240 --> 04:26.070
For your sake,

04:26.920 --> 04:28.750
he cut off the hand of Li Qi, Biantang's

04:28.750 --> 04:30.070
General of Cavalry.

04:30.390 --> 04:31.240
Tell me,

04:31.980 --> 04:34.070
whose tab does that hand go on—

04:34.600 --> 04:36.190
Yan Xun's or yours?

04:36.190 --> 04:38.190
Yan Xun is brutal and bloodthirsty.

04:38.320 --> 04:39.920
He's unfit to rule Great Yan.

04:40.070 --> 04:41.200
And what about Li Ce?

04:41.240 --> 04:43.360
He was meant to live in luxury
as Crown Prince.

04:43.360 --> 04:44.920
Had you not fought against the Empress
on his behalf,

04:44.920 --> 04:46.920
how would he have ended up like this?

04:47.240 --> 04:48.000
Chun'er,

04:49.180 --> 04:50.870
I know you carry much hatred and pain

04:50.870 --> 04:52.070
in your heart.

04:53.270 --> 04:55.310
And you've endured things
you shouldn't have.

04:55.310 --> 04:56.750
But if you remain stuck in the past,

04:56.750 --> 04:59.409
you'll only sink deeper into it
and suffer more.

05:02.160 --> 05:03.480
I never understood

05:04.560 --> 05:06.390
why I hated you so much.

05:07.560 --> 05:08.240
I think

05:09.450 --> 05:11.210
it must be out of jealousy.

05:12.720 --> 05:13.630
It's over now.

05:14.040 --> 05:15.310
They're all dead!

05:15.480 --> 05:16.390
I'll take you out of here.

05:16.390 --> 05:17.450
I'll take you home!

05:17.500 --> 05:18.980
I'll kill you!

05:19.390 --> 05:20.560
I'll kill you!

05:23.680 --> 05:24.510
I'm sorry.

05:28.960 --> 05:32.230
I hate you. I hate you! I hate you!

05:32.260 --> 05:33.670
I hate you!

05:34.120 --> 05:35.680
They're all dead!

05:35.800 --> 05:37.310
You killed them all!

05:38.170 --> 05:38.850
Chun'er!

05:40.240 --> 05:41.170
Don't be afraid!

05:54.090 --> 05:56.409
I was born a noble and precious princess.

05:57.890 --> 05:59.490
I seemed to have everything,

06:00.840 --> 06:03.840
but in fact, I have nothing.

06:05.190 --> 06:07.800
Even my father's love for me is fake.

06:08.440 --> 06:10.270
You were nothing but a slave,

06:10.290 --> 06:11.950
yet here you stand above us all,

06:11.950 --> 06:13.680
with everything I ever wanted.

06:14.040 --> 06:16.390
I just want to see you suffer
with my own eyes—

06:16.390 --> 06:17.870
to watch you lose everything

06:17.870 --> 06:19.560
and everyone you care about!

06:22.240 --> 06:23.370
You're blessed with

06:24.160 --> 06:26.240
a beauty everyone envies.

06:26.880 --> 06:29.010
You could've lived a much better life.

06:29.750 --> 06:30.480
I know

06:31.320 --> 06:33.340
you feel that Yan Xun and I
have made you suffer.

06:33.340 --> 06:35.070
Your mother and your father—

06:35.159 --> 06:36.750
you think they've wronged you too.

06:36.750 --> 06:39.880
You think fate and this world
have treated you unfairly.

06:40.240 --> 06:42.040
You believe you were born to
live in luxury

06:42.040 --> 06:43.480
and stand above the masses.

06:43.480 --> 06:45.120
But that was a gift from fate.

06:45.630 --> 06:46.690
You didn't cherish it.

06:46.690 --> 06:48.240
Instead, you chose to use it for revenge—

06:48.240 --> 06:49.840
revenge against me, a slave,

06:49.980 --> 06:50.909
against Yan Xun,

06:51.190 --> 06:52.450
and against everyone,

06:52.680 --> 06:54.070
including yourself.

06:55.720 --> 06:56.600
Was it worth it?

07:03.750 --> 07:04.600
Yes!

07:08.070 --> 07:09.270
I just hate you.

07:10.750 --> 07:12.480
I want revenge on you.

07:12.720 --> 07:15.870
Please drink less of my wedding wine,
Princess Consort of Luo.

07:15.870 --> 07:17.870
Too much wine is bad for your health.

09:05.360 --> 09:07.220
The members of the delegation...

09:08.720 --> 09:10.250
were seized by the Empress.

09:10.600 --> 09:12.630
Only Baze and I managed to escape.

09:13.240 --> 09:14.240
I asked Baze...

09:15.360 --> 09:15.840
to go to

09:16.120 --> 09:16.910
Ximeng

09:17.270 --> 09:18.470
to deliver a message.

09:20.390 --> 09:20.960
Lingyue.

09:28.630 --> 09:30.030
How are things with Li Ce?

09:31.900 --> 09:33.160
He's indeed in prison.

09:33.870 --> 09:36.550
Lin Mu and Song Cheng were also captured
along with him.

09:36.550 --> 09:38.150
On the day it happened,

09:38.630 --> 09:41.000
I wasn't at the restaurant,
so I avoided it.

09:41.000 --> 09:43.860
They knew you would never abandon
the Crown Prince.

09:44.270 --> 09:45.810
It was all just to lure you back.

09:44.300 --> 09:46.950
[Mihe Abode]

09:47.440 --> 09:48.300
Your Highness!

09:53.000 --> 09:53.860
Your Highness,

09:53.910 --> 09:55.390
there is a carriage
from Great Yan outside.

09:55.390 --> 09:57.190
They say they're here to see you.

10:25.000 --> 10:25.630
Chu.

10:26.510 --> 10:28.940
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

10:28.960 --> 10:31.640
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

10:31.550 --> 10:32.200
Chu.

10:31.870 --> 10:33.050
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

10:33.070 --> 10:34.550
♪ My longing surges ♪

10:34.760 --> 10:37.170
♪ I become haggard ♪

10:35.000 --> 10:37.970
These are my old clothes
from when I was the Heir Apparent.

10:37.970 --> 10:39.920
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

10:38.630 --> 10:40.350
I didn't expect them to still fit.

10:40.350 --> 10:42.770
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

10:41.150 --> 10:41.840
Chu,

10:41.960 --> 10:43.840
I especially put on this outfit today

10:43.200 --> 10:44.770
♪ My love remains ♪

10:44.670 --> 10:46.510
because I wanted to see you
in this identity.

10:44.990 --> 10:48.520
♪ But you're already gone ♪

10:46.960 --> 10:48.390
Right now, I'm not the King of Great Yan.

10:48.390 --> 10:50.670
I'm just a hostage prince
trapped in Zhenhuangcheng.

10:48.770 --> 10:50.390
♪ What I seek in life ♪

10:50.830 --> 10:52.200
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

10:51.000 --> 10:51.670
Chu,

10:52.280 --> 10:54.270
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

10:53.150 --> 10:54.750
could you, even if just for a moment,

10:54.750 --> 10:56.290
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

10:55.750 --> 10:57.870
be the slave Chu Qiao
trapped in Qingshan Manor?

10:56.580 --> 10:59.770
♪ My longing still rests ♪

10:59.480 --> 11:00.630
I want to take you somewhere.

10:59.960 --> 11:02.140
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

11:02.260 --> 11:03.840
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

11:03.870 --> 11:06.350
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

11:06.600 --> 11:11.000
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

11:11.370 --> 11:12.720
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

11:12.740 --> 11:15.010
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

11:15.030 --> 11:17.460
♪ How do we start over? ♪

11:17.530 --> 11:20.400
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

11:20.420 --> 11:23.170
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

11:23.280 --> 11:26.120
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

11:26.150 --> 11:29.070
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

11:29.090 --> 11:31.820
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

11:31.940 --> 11:34.240
♪ In the end ♪

11:52.160 --> 11:53.320
-Make way!
-Make way!

11:53.320 --> 11:54.780
-Make way!
-Out of the way!

11:55.240 --> 11:56.720
Who has the nerve to block the city gate?

11:56.720 --> 11:57.380
Arrest her!

12:03.270 --> 12:04.670
I'm the Consort of the King of Great Yan.

12:04.670 --> 12:06.000
Take me to see him.

12:07.000 --> 12:07.660
Consort of Great Yan?

12:07.660 --> 12:09.190
Hurry! Prepare a carriage!

12:09.960 --> 12:12.360
-Prepare a carriage!
-Prepare a carriage!

12:16.370 --> 12:17.130
Make way!

12:20.240 --> 12:21.090
Make way!

12:48.750 --> 12:50.150
Why did you bring me here?

12:55.200 --> 12:56.120
This ribbon

12:56.750 --> 12:59.920
is part of a tradition among the people
of Mount Huihui in Great Yan.

12:59.920 --> 13:00.850
When I was young,

13:01.390 --> 13:03.390
my mother often stayed there.

13:04.360 --> 13:04.910
She told me

13:04.910 --> 13:07.310
that the people of Mount Huihui
in Great Yan

13:07.870 --> 13:09.200
would hang this ribbon,

13:09.670 --> 13:11.600
along with this wishing plaque...

13:13.440 --> 13:15.320
on this wishing tree.

13:16.120 --> 13:16.870
Then the wind

13:17.870 --> 13:20.270
would carry their wishes
high into the sky,

13:20.360 --> 13:22.640
and their wishes could come true.

13:37.720 --> 13:38.440
Chu.

13:41.080 --> 13:42.610
Forget our pain and sorrow.

13:43.240 --> 13:44.900
Come back to Great Yan with me.

13:45.360 --> 13:46.510
I once promised you

13:47.150 --> 13:47.950
that Great Yan

13:48.550 --> 13:49.950
will always be your home.

13:50.970 --> 13:51.650
Chu,

13:52.320 --> 13:53.840
we used to be so close

13:54.360 --> 13:56.300
that we could entrust our lives
to each other.

13:56.300 --> 13:57.200
After losing you,

13:57.200 --> 13:59.460
it feels as though I lost the whole world.

13:59.720 --> 14:00.850
Only if you come back

14:01.910 --> 14:03.270
can I find myself again.

14:09.280 --> 14:09.920
Yan Xun,

14:10.750 --> 14:11.630
I know you

14:12.790 --> 14:14.360
just as you know me.

14:19.680 --> 14:20.410
Chu?

14:21.020 --> 14:22.590
Stop pretending.

14:22.750 --> 14:23.810
What you feel for me

14:24.670 --> 14:27.030
is nothing more than a desire
to conquer and possess.

14:27.030 --> 14:29.090
If you truly had any affection for me,

14:29.390 --> 14:30.270
Miss Zhong,

14:30.630 --> 14:32.240
those people
from the Universal Harmony Guild,

14:32.240 --> 14:33.200
and Huan Huan

14:34.240 --> 14:36.100
would not have died by your sword.

14:36.840 --> 14:38.170
Zhao Chun'er was right.

14:38.270 --> 14:39.200
My mistake

14:40.270 --> 14:42.600
was believing in your feelings back then.

14:43.600 --> 14:46.630
Now I'll correct that mistake
with my own hands.

14:48.840 --> 14:49.550
Chu,

14:49.680 --> 14:51.940
can you really bring yourself to kill me?

14:52.790 --> 14:54.630
If you truly wanted to,

14:55.080 --> 14:58.200
you would've done it by the frozen lake.

15:13.450 --> 15:14.900
You poisoned me...

15:15.510 --> 15:16.510
Don't worry, Chu.

15:18.000 --> 15:20.560
Just some sedative incense
that suppresses your inner power.

15:20.560 --> 15:22.820
It will wear off on its own
within an hour.

15:23.480 --> 15:25.240
Don't try my patience.

15:26.030 --> 15:26.870
You're right.

15:27.080 --> 15:28.150
You know me

15:29.270 --> 15:30.870
just as I know you.

15:31.960 --> 15:33.960
That's why I made preparations in advance.

15:33.960 --> 15:35.720
I can kill you anytime.

15:40.170 --> 15:40.800
However,

15:41.560 --> 15:43.080
I won't kill you.

15:43.850 --> 15:45.360
Three days from now, I want you

15:45.360 --> 15:47.240
to appear at the gates
of the Crown Prince's Mansion

15:47.240 --> 15:49.840
wearing the bridal robes
of the Queen of Great Yan.

15:49.840 --> 15:50.650
Otherwise,

15:51.840 --> 15:54.040
I'll destroy everything you hold dear.

15:55.200 --> 15:57.030
That Crown Prince of Biantang,

15:58.120 --> 16:00.030
anyone who follows you,
or anyone you care about—

16:00.030 --> 16:01.480
I will spare none of them.

16:02.200 --> 16:03.660
I'll make every single one

16:04.080 --> 16:04.910
of them

16:05.960 --> 16:08.480
wish they were dead.

16:12.690 --> 16:14.990
[King of Great Yan's Travelling Residence]

16:29.180 --> 16:29.980
Your Majesty.

16:30.340 --> 16:31.200
What happened?

16:31.390 --> 16:32.590
Come with me quickly.

16:47.730 --> 16:48.580
Your Majesty.

17:02.790 --> 17:03.270
Consort Helian

17:03.270 --> 17:05.930
was brought here
by the guards at Yingtian Gate.

17:06.440 --> 17:08.230
They said she fainted at the city gate

17:08.230 --> 17:10.230
because she had ridden for too long,

17:11.170 --> 17:13.930
traveling day and night without rest,
leaving her body weakened.

17:13.930 --> 17:15.200
Why did she come here?

17:15.550 --> 17:16.270
Most likely, she heard

17:16.270 --> 17:18.730
that Your Majesty is going to
marry Queen Chu

17:19.349 --> 17:20.510
and panicked.

17:25.829 --> 17:26.630
Your Majesty.

17:32.430 --> 17:33.230
Your Majesty.

17:34.910 --> 17:36.770
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

17:39.000 --> 17:40.640
I know I was wrong.

17:57.720 --> 17:58.680
I know

17:59.400 --> 18:01.060
Your Majesty loves Queen Chu.

18:01.480 --> 18:04.110
I would never dare compete with her
for your affection,

18:04.110 --> 18:06.270
nor would I do anything to harm her.

18:06.620 --> 18:07.940
I was just afraid...

18:10.590 --> 18:12.990
afraid that once Your Majesty marries her,

18:14.390 --> 18:15.780
you would abandon me.

18:16.180 --> 18:18.510
I only beg Your Majesty
not to send me away.

18:18.590 --> 18:22.200
Let me stay and serve you and Queen Chu.

18:25.880 --> 18:26.680
Your Majesty!

18:29.090 --> 18:29.810
Cheng Yuan.

18:31.510 --> 18:33.040
Consort Helian is injured.

18:34.240 --> 18:35.970
Find two maids to attend to her.

18:36.050 --> 18:36.660
Yes.

19:19.960 --> 19:21.030
What do you think Zhuge Yue

19:21.030 --> 19:23.430
means by bringing back
a woman from Ximeng?

19:24.030 --> 19:27.200
This courtyard was left to Princess Fu
by the Crown Prince.

19:27.200 --> 19:29.060
The Princess told us to meet here.

19:29.510 --> 19:30.240
But look at him—

19:30.240 --> 19:32.500
he brought back some ugly foreign woman.

19:38.590 --> 19:39.240
What are you doing?

19:39.240 --> 19:39.880
Stop it!

19:40.590 --> 19:43.250
I'm thinking of a way
to rescue the Crown Prince.

19:43.510 --> 19:44.160
You...

19:44.920 --> 19:45.880
Wang Shi'er,

19:45.920 --> 19:47.290
why don't you dig a tunnel right here

19:47.290 --> 19:49.210
and dig His Highness out?

19:50.310 --> 19:51.170
How about that?

19:51.310 --> 19:52.910
That's the Imperial Prison—

19:53.240 --> 19:55.030
the most secure prison in this country.

19:55.030 --> 19:57.490
Tight security
isn't the only problem here.

19:57.680 --> 19:58.740
Bad news! Bad news!

19:59.240 --> 20:01.130
Miss Chu is going to be married off
to Great Yan!

20:01.130 --> 20:02.060
What did you say?

20:02.510 --> 20:04.840
Miss Chu is being married off
to Great Yan!

20:05.910 --> 20:07.770
-"Married off?"
-"Married off?"

20:08.920 --> 20:10.680
Could it be that the Princess plans to
use this marriage

20:10.680 --> 20:12.750
to call on Great Yan's Black Eagle Army
to save His Highness?

20:12.750 --> 20:14.350
I actually think this method could work.

20:14.350 --> 20:15.280
It's worth a try.

20:15.440 --> 20:16.440
At a time like this,

20:16.440 --> 20:17.680
you're still in the mood to joke?

20:17.680 --> 20:18.750
How else could it be?

20:18.750 --> 20:21.640
How could the Princess possibly agree to
some marriage alliance?

20:21.640 --> 20:23.170
What are you talking about?

20:27.460 --> 20:28.260
Young Master,

20:28.350 --> 20:30.270
did you know Yan Xun is going to
marry Miss Chu?

20:30.270 --> 20:33.530
The Biantang Empress has already issued
a decree for this.

20:33.890 --> 20:35.680
I heard about it on my way here.

20:35.750 --> 20:36.880
Aren't you worried?

20:37.290 --> 20:39.480
I'd just intended to go to
the Crown Prince's Mansion to see Miss Chu,

20:39.480 --> 20:40.440
but I heard that early this morning,

20:40.440 --> 20:41.640
she went out with Yan Xun

20:41.640 --> 20:42.910
and hasn't returned yet.

20:42.910 --> 20:44.910
Didn't we agree to meet here?

20:45.310 --> 20:46.680
But it's been two days.

20:46.920 --> 20:47.800
Miss Chu...

20:55.830 --> 20:57.690
I just went to the Imperial Prison

20:58.000 --> 20:59.480
to find a way to see Li Ce.

20:59.750 --> 21:01.220
However, the Empress has given her orders.

21:01.220 --> 21:02.550
No one dared to let me in.

21:02.570 --> 21:05.200
Li Ce is currently charged with
regicide and treason.

21:05.200 --> 21:06.480
Naturally, the Empress
has countless reasons

21:06.480 --> 21:07.750
to bar anyone from seeing him.

21:07.750 --> 21:08.990
If I'm not mistaken,

21:09.640 --> 21:11.720
her next move will likely be to use Li Ce

21:11.720 --> 21:12.750
to force you to leave here.

21:12.750 --> 21:15.010
You know that I'm to marry into Great Yan?

21:15.790 --> 21:17.350
This is the Empress's scheme.

21:17.350 --> 21:18.810
If we want to save Li Ce now,

21:19.030 --> 21:20.640
we can only clear his name.

21:21.480 --> 21:22.750
The case of
the Crown Prince assassinating the Emperor

21:22.750 --> 21:24.790
is riddled with
suspicious inconsistencies.

21:24.790 --> 21:26.480
The assassin took his own life on the spot

21:26.480 --> 21:27.940
after the attempt failed.

21:28.310 --> 21:31.110
We have no way to begin
if we wish to reopen the case.

21:34.070 --> 21:36.070
I know where the assassin's body is.

21:36.640 --> 21:38.720
The death row inmates
and felons in Tangjing,

21:38.720 --> 21:39.550
after death, are all buried

21:39.550 --> 21:41.470
outside a fir grove
in the west of the city.

21:41.470 --> 21:42.930
That place is a mass grave.

21:43.030 --> 21:44.160
I can take you there.

21:50.710 --> 21:51.440
General Sun.

21:57.480 --> 21:58.270
General Sun.

21:58.770 --> 21:59.900
General Sun.

22:00.510 --> 22:02.920
What brings you here, General Sun?

22:03.320 --> 22:03.920
Someone,

22:03.950 --> 22:05.200
serve tea to General Sun.

22:05.200 --> 22:05.760
No need.

22:06.240 --> 22:06.830
Lord Zuo,

22:07.160 --> 22:09.000
I came today for a case file.

22:09.240 --> 22:11.030
Give it to me, and I'll be on my way.

22:11.030 --> 22:12.960
I won't keep you from your fine tea.

22:13.640 --> 22:14.640
What kind of file

22:14.640 --> 22:16.920
is important enough for you
to come in person?

22:16.920 --> 22:17.720
You could've simply

22:17.720 --> 22:18.960
sent someone here.

22:18.960 --> 22:22.690
The case of the assassination attempt
on His Majesty a few days ago.

22:25.360 --> 22:26.090
General Sun,

22:26.340 --> 22:28.770
this file was taken by the higher-ups.

22:30.790 --> 22:31.480
Then...

22:32.000 --> 22:33.070
I'll take my leave.

22:33.550 --> 22:35.080
Sorry for the disturbance.

22:35.400 --> 22:36.730
Take care, General Sun.

22:43.510 --> 22:45.070
Go report to Lord Zhan.

22:46.830 --> 22:48.830
Tell him that General Sun came here.

22:49.380 --> 22:49.940
Yes.

23:00.550 --> 23:02.790
Didn't Xiao Ran say
her injuries weren't severe?

23:02.790 --> 23:05.510
Why hasn't she woken up
after a whole day and night?

23:05.510 --> 23:07.000
Although her current injuries
are not severe,

23:07.000 --> 23:09.310
her old wounds haven't fully healed yet.

23:10.110 --> 23:10.910
On top of that,

23:11.500 --> 23:13.000
her body has long been worn out.

23:13.000 --> 23:14.160
New injuries compounding old wounds—

23:14.160 --> 23:16.220
that's why she's still unconscious.

23:28.440 --> 23:30.150
Isn't she the Queen of the Lingyue Clan?

23:30.150 --> 23:31.960
Why does she have so many old wounds?

23:31.960 --> 23:34.960
Even the spies of Qingshan Manor
didn't have this many scars.

23:34.960 --> 23:36.770
After the Lingyue Clan was conquered
by King Ximeng,

23:36.770 --> 23:38.770
she was nothing more than his slave.

23:39.000 --> 23:42.000
Many of the things she did
were not of her own choosing.

23:42.310 --> 23:43.680
Do you remember what Qingshan Manor

23:43.680 --> 23:44.720
used to be like?

23:45.510 --> 23:47.710
Ximeng is like a larger Qingshan Manor—

23:47.880 --> 23:50.160
or an even crueler one.

23:50.960 --> 23:52.560
Although she's from Ximeng,

23:53.070 --> 23:54.870
she fell into the Empress's trap

23:54.870 --> 23:56.880
because she was helping me save He Xiao.

23:56.880 --> 23:57.750
No matter what,

23:58.270 --> 24:00.730
I must make sure
she leaves Biantang safely.

24:30.830 --> 24:32.090
This is the mass grave.

24:32.680 --> 24:33.830
In Tangjing,

24:34.000 --> 24:36.070
criminals executed for their crimes,

24:36.070 --> 24:37.750
along with unclaimed bodies,

24:37.750 --> 24:39.440
are sent to be buried here.

24:40.000 --> 24:41.510
According to the rules,
the assassin's body

24:41.510 --> 24:42.680
should be somewhere nearby.

24:42.680 --> 24:43.640
Let's search the mounds one by one.

24:43.640 --> 24:44.270
No need.

24:44.450 --> 24:45.240
He was buried not long ago.

24:45.240 --> 24:47.250
We can just check the color of the dirt,

24:47.250 --> 24:48.850
and we'll find it right away.

24:49.430 --> 24:50.080
Let's go.

24:54.000 --> 24:55.920
Sorry for the disturbance. Sorry.

24:55.920 --> 24:57.750
Sorry, sorry.

24:57.930 --> 24:59.410
Please don't blame me.

24:59.790 --> 25:01.830
Sorry for the disturbance.

25:02.750 --> 25:04.270
Didn't you say you don't believe in
this sort of thing?

25:04.270 --> 25:05.270
Why are you bowing?

25:05.270 --> 25:06.440
The graves I used to rob

25:06.440 --> 25:08.310
all belonged to nobles and aristocrats—

25:08.310 --> 25:10.720
even the lowest-ranking among them
were third-rank officials.

25:10.720 --> 25:11.440
There isn't

25:11.440 --> 25:12.900
even a decent coffin here.

25:13.240 --> 25:14.920
I'm afraid of being haunted
by some ghosts of paupers,

25:14.920 --> 25:16.380
so I'm paying my respects.

25:17.920 --> 25:19.450
Sorry for the disturbance.

25:19.960 --> 25:20.750
The burial mounds in this area

25:20.750 --> 25:22.070
are all from long ago.

25:22.480 --> 25:25.080
The soil has settled into
thick, distinct layers.

25:25.080 --> 25:27.740
Only this one shows no signs
of being disturbed.

25:28.720 --> 25:30.270
This mound here is looser.

25:30.750 --> 25:32.070
It looks newly dug.

25:33.830 --> 25:34.630
What's wrong?

25:36.550 --> 25:37.340
The soil has already dried,

25:37.340 --> 25:38.590
and the smell of blood has faded.

25:38.590 --> 25:40.200
It should be from about a month ago.

25:40.200 --> 25:41.860
Not the one we are looking for.

25:59.550 --> 26:00.370
What are you doing?

26:00.370 --> 26:01.970
It's not often I come across someone
in my line of work.

26:01.970 --> 26:02.960
I thought I'd exchange some pointers
with him.

26:02.960 --> 26:05.090
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

26:06.940 --> 26:08.070
Find a place to hide.

26:08.240 --> 26:09.160
Stay out of sight

26:09.160 --> 26:10.020
and be careful.

26:24.310 --> 26:25.510
Darn it.

26:27.200 --> 26:28.680
It's completely charred.

26:29.640 --> 26:31.240
What can I find out from this?

26:39.830 --> 26:41.200
Why are there three people here?

26:41.200 --> 26:42.720
Which one is Sun Di?

26:42.960 --> 26:43.830
I can't tell.

26:44.240 --> 26:46.170
Let's kill all three of them, then.

26:53.430 --> 26:54.270
General Sun.

26:54.300 --> 26:55.110
Princess Fu?

26:55.240 --> 26:56.200
Why are you here?

26:56.490 --> 26:58.590
I assume we're all here
on account of the Crown Prince.

26:58.590 --> 27:00.390
The assassin's body is charred.

27:01.010 --> 27:02.210
It's pointless now.

27:03.440 --> 27:03.830
No.

27:04.160 --> 27:04.820
It's a trap.

27:22.270 --> 27:22.920
Speak.

27:23.110 --> 27:24.310
Who sent you?

27:24.350 --> 27:25.070
Lord Zhan!

27:25.120 --> 27:26.320
Lord Zhan sent us!

27:26.720 --> 27:28.000
Then there's no need to keep them alive.

27:28.000 --> 27:29.330
We should kill them all.

27:30.000 --> 27:30.960
-No!
-Don't kill me!

27:30.960 --> 27:32.110
-Spare us!
-Please spare us!

27:32.110 --> 27:33.140
-Don't!
-Please spare us!

27:33.140 --> 27:34.180
Spare us!

27:42.050 --> 27:43.680
Hurry! Run!

28:01.440 --> 28:02.750
Greetings, Miss Chu.

28:04.860 --> 28:05.690
General Sun,

28:06.070 --> 28:07.000
I'm Princess Fu.

28:07.240 --> 28:09.030
You don't need to hide who you really are.

28:09.030 --> 28:11.200
When I accompanied the Crown Prince
on a diplomatic mission to Great Yong,

28:11.200 --> 28:12.800
I saw you in Zhenhuangcheng.

28:13.070 --> 28:14.350
You might not remember me,

28:14.350 --> 28:16.230
but you left a deep impression on me.

28:16.230 --> 28:18.960
You were the martial arts instructor
for Great Yong's imperial guards.

28:18.960 --> 28:19.880
So,

28:19.960 --> 28:21.590
you've known who I am all this time.

28:21.590 --> 28:23.070
But you never went to
the Emperor or the Empress

28:23.070 --> 28:24.330
to reveal my identity.

28:24.510 --> 28:26.310
It was just a suspicion at first,

28:26.830 --> 28:29.560
but crossing blades with you today
confirmed it.

28:29.750 --> 28:31.560
I'd thought that
when the Crown Prince fell into trouble,

28:31.560 --> 28:33.240
you would take the opportunity
to slip away.

28:33.240 --> 28:34.500
But I didn't expect you

28:34.750 --> 28:36.880
to risk your life for the Crown Prince.

28:37.110 --> 28:40.110
I truly admire
your deep affection for him.

28:42.160 --> 28:43.980
General Sun, you misunderstand.

28:43.980 --> 28:45.370
His Highness once
showed me great kindness,

28:45.370 --> 28:46.630
so naturally I must...

28:47.120 --> 28:49.250
I naturally understand what you mean.

28:49.300 --> 28:50.450
After all, gratitude

28:50.450 --> 28:52.520
is often where love takes root.

28:53.600 --> 28:57.400
Although His Highness once behaved
rather frivolously toward you,

28:57.570 --> 28:59.030
time reveals a person's true character.

28:59.030 --> 29:01.070
I trust that after enduring hardship

29:01.070 --> 29:02.640
side by side with you,

29:03.110 --> 29:05.400
His Highness must be
deeply in love with you.

29:05.400 --> 29:08.860
I look forward to raising a glass
at your wedding in the future.

29:12.280 --> 29:13.040
General Sun,

29:13.310 --> 29:15.790
you just said
you came for the Crown Prince today.

29:15.790 --> 29:18.020
Does that mean you also believe
there is something suspicious about this?

29:18.020 --> 29:19.950
Yes. I was just about to get to that.

29:20.480 --> 29:22.900
The day
after His Majesty was assassinated,

29:22.900 --> 29:24.850
I happened to be
at the Ministry of Justice.

29:24.850 --> 29:26.920
I didn't want to bring it up
to anyone again,

29:26.920 --> 29:29.440
but since it concerns the Crown Prince,

29:29.470 --> 29:30.800
I won't hide it anymore.

29:31.280 --> 29:33.310
Fifteen years ago, when I was ordered

29:33.310 --> 29:36.240
to suppress the Nanxi Tribe
in the southwest of Biantang,

29:36.240 --> 29:37.500
I had seen that tattoo.

29:37.510 --> 29:38.590
The Nanxi people?

29:38.760 --> 29:39.200
Yes.

29:39.440 --> 29:40.380
The Nanxi Tribe

29:40.480 --> 29:42.740
lived in the mountains west of Biantang.

29:42.750 --> 29:43.950
Their land was barren

29:44.030 --> 29:45.280
and not suited for farming,

29:45.280 --> 29:49.100
so they frequently raided the borderlands
of Biantang for goods and valuables.

29:49.100 --> 29:51.430
His Majesty ordered me to drive them away.

29:51.720 --> 29:53.200
Though few in number,

29:53.480 --> 29:55.140
they were cunning and fierce.

29:55.990 --> 29:58.880
After several clashes,
we still couldn't defeat them.

29:58.880 --> 30:00.830
To relieve His Majesty's worries,
Her Majesty

30:00.830 --> 30:02.090
issued a secret edict,

30:02.290 --> 30:05.760
ordering me to set fire
to the Nanxi Tribe's villages.

30:16.000 --> 30:16.730
General Sun,

30:16.790 --> 30:18.680
we've already sealed off the only exits

30:18.680 --> 30:19.750
of the nearby villages with fire.

30:19.750 --> 30:21.270
It should be hard for anyone to escape.

30:21.270 --> 30:22.590
Should we stay here and keep watch

30:22.590 --> 30:24.390
or leave after the fire goes out?

30:24.750 --> 30:26.830
Let's go. No need to keep watch.

30:28.680 --> 30:31.400
The Nanxi people lived in wooden buildings
for generations.

30:31.400 --> 30:34.030
Once the fire started,
it spread through everything.

30:34.030 --> 30:34.920
After that day,

30:35.590 --> 30:37.720
very few Nanxi people survived.

30:37.720 --> 30:40.790
The entire tribe vanished after that.

30:41.900 --> 30:44.100
I didn't want to carry out such an order,

30:44.170 --> 30:46.500
but I had no choice
but to obey the Empress.

30:46.720 --> 30:47.650
So you're saying

30:48.750 --> 30:51.080
that the tattoo is the Nanxi Tribe's mark,

30:51.510 --> 30:54.350
and the assassin was a Nanxi survivor?

30:54.750 --> 30:57.920
The Nanxi Tribe was wiped out
over 10 years ago.

30:58.350 --> 30:59.720
For one to suddenly appear now

30:59.720 --> 31:02.000
and be claimed to
have acted on the Crown Prince's orders—

31:02.000 --> 31:03.530
that simply does not add up.

31:05.030 --> 31:05.680
Miss Chu,

31:06.030 --> 31:08.110
you've spent day and night
at the Crown Prince's side,

31:08.110 --> 31:09.570
closer to him than anyone.

31:09.720 --> 31:11.340
You must believe more than I do

31:11.340 --> 31:13.170
that the Crown Prince couldn't possibly
have had any connection

31:13.170 --> 31:14.830
with the Nanxi people, right?

31:17.120 --> 31:18.720
Why are you always coughing?

31:19.480 --> 31:20.920
Miss, who is this?

31:21.670 --> 31:22.540
He is...

31:22.790 --> 31:23.440
A guard.

31:25.810 --> 31:26.650
A guard?

31:26.680 --> 31:28.090
I'm General Chu's guard,

31:28.780 --> 31:30.520
responsible for her safety.

31:34.590 --> 31:36.920
When I crossed blades with you earlier
in the mass grave,

31:36.920 --> 31:39.070
I could tell you were quite skilled.

31:41.400 --> 31:42.580
Are you interested

31:42.720 --> 31:45.000
in taking a post in our Tang Army?

31:49.030 --> 31:50.880
You don't need to look at the Princess.

31:50.880 --> 31:52.550
No matter how much she pays you,

31:52.550 --> 31:54.880
I'll pay three times as much.
How about it?

31:56.430 --> 31:57.020
Zhu...

31:59.480 --> 32:00.070
Guard,

32:00.250 --> 32:01.380
what do you think?

32:04.510 --> 32:06.730
Thank you for your appreciation,
General Sun.

32:06.730 --> 32:09.800
However, I'm not only
the Princess's guard,

32:10.790 --> 32:11.880
but I also have...

32:14.030 --> 32:15.630
some personal ties with her,

32:18.680 --> 32:21.140
which makes it inconvenient for me
to leave.

32:25.830 --> 32:27.690
Miss, you and the Crown Prince...

32:28.070 --> 32:29.640
How come you and a guard...

32:33.030 --> 32:34.430
I'm not a refined person.

32:34.590 --> 32:35.640
I don't understand

32:35.640 --> 32:37.270
all these romantic entanglements of yours.

32:37.270 --> 32:38.200
I'll leave

32:38.680 --> 32:39.810
this token with you.

32:40.110 --> 32:41.240
If there's anything

32:41.350 --> 32:43.010
concerning the Crown Prince,

32:43.030 --> 32:44.680
you can come to my residence at any time.

32:44.680 --> 32:45.550
Thank you, General Sun.

32:45.550 --> 32:46.240
I'll take my leave.

32:46.240 --> 32:47.270
General Sun, I'll walk you out.

32:47.270 --> 32:47.960
No need.

32:48.110 --> 32:48.640
No, let me walk you out.

32:48.640 --> 32:49.480
No need.

32:49.510 --> 32:50.240
General Sun,

32:50.640 --> 32:51.640
I'll walk you out.

32:57.600 --> 32:59.310
Just as Your Majesty predicted,

32:59.310 --> 33:00.720
General Sun really went to examine

33:00.720 --> 33:03.180
the assassin's remains
in the dead of night.

33:03.640 --> 33:05.110
However, there was

33:05.550 --> 33:07.310
another group there besides him.

33:07.310 --> 33:08.200
Who else?

33:09.200 --> 33:10.800
Our men failed to catch them.

33:11.240 --> 33:14.110
But at this point, aside from Princess Fu,

33:14.110 --> 33:15.440
no one

33:15.570 --> 33:17.430
will try to save the Crown Prince.

33:21.550 --> 33:22.250
Never mind.

33:22.920 --> 33:24.760
Let her run into a few more setbacks,

33:24.760 --> 33:26.110
and she'll fall in line.

33:27.920 --> 33:29.160
I'm just worried

33:30.070 --> 33:31.330
that Princess Fu won't

33:31.680 --> 33:33.740
easily agree to marry into Great Yan.

33:33.960 --> 33:35.000
Rest assured.

33:36.550 --> 33:38.350
Since she came back to save Li Ce,

33:39.640 --> 33:41.900
she will naturally accept the marriage—

33:43.130 --> 33:44.850
as long as we make her

33:45.440 --> 33:47.270
an offer she cannot refuse.

34:08.440 --> 34:09.920
Zhuge Yue, wake up.

34:10.000 --> 34:10.800
Zhuge Yue.

34:10.800 --> 34:11.929
Your Highness, run!

34:12.920 --> 34:14.440
I want you to suffer.

34:14.630 --> 34:16.230
I'm willing to spend the rest of my life
fasting and doing good deeds,

34:16.230 --> 34:18.880
asking only that His Majesty
and his beloved may live in happiness.

34:18.880 --> 34:20.280
Our interests are aligned.

34:20.280 --> 34:21.650
We can bury our past grudges

34:21.650 --> 34:22.760
and discuss a partnership.

34:22.760 --> 34:24.620
If you don't want to marry Yan Xun,

34:24.800 --> 34:26.670
you can choose to side with me.
